啃自己的老本，(눈 _ 눈)，唉） 然后现在就在考虑大学可能会用到的东西，预算的话不知道有没有三千，因为到时候结果出来后，家里包括亲戚会封红包，但是那个要用来交学费，家里也并没有什么钱，所以给的可能也不多。 买笔记本的话主要是考虑预算不够的话，一般的笔记本很容易卡。以前上网课的时候题主好朋友因为之前的台式坏了，所以买了两三千的笔记本，然后没用两年巨卡（题主亲自体验过），而且朋友也并没有下什么游戏。题主是想如果真的买了的话是打算会用很久的。 如果买平板的话是因为觉得方便，但是题主并没有用过平板，题主一般用手机或者电脑比较多，所以很纠结 (｡•ˇ‸ˇ•｡) 所以希望能够得到知友们的一些建议呀，或者给题主分享一下上大学要准备的东西，因为填的学校离家都不是很近，回家会很麻烦，想要提前先准备齐全了。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610474097"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I2pWfz5vUvskSEAMaCDk3OTQxODEwINbLlKUGMAA4Z0AXcgk2MTA0NzQwOTd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1688656162.61799", "card_id": "Q_608695342", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 68}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大夏天的没什么胃口，有什么又开胃做法又简单的菜？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-714a51bf8c0e72d87bc48bcf01340477_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/608695342"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2pWfz5vUvskSEAMaCDk3NTQ2MjQ5IM6Y5KQGMAA4jgFAGHIJNjA4Njk1MzQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "25_1688656162.62079", "card_id": "Q_610358729", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 129}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么年龄越大越沉默？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "49 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/610358729"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I2pWfz5vUvskSEAMaCDk3OTE2MjEyIJvIkKUGMAA4uwFAGX